=== Bold
--- creole
I **like** Mike.
--- html
<p>I <strong>like</strong> Mike.</p>

=== Bold and whitespace
--- creole
I** like    **Mike.
--- html
<p>I<strong> like    </strong>Mike.</p>

=== Bold in a list
--- creole
* **foo**
--- html
<ul>
<li><strong>foo</strong></li>
</ul>

=== Bold not in a header
--- creole
= **foo**
--- html
<h1>**foo**</h1>

